data.meta_description: Find the perfect beachfront home rental for your trip to Karlshamn Municipality. Pet-friendly beachfront home rentals, beachfront home rentals with a pool, private beachfront home rentals, and luxury beachfront home rentals. Find and book unique beachfront homes on Airbnb.

Beautiful right by the ocean.

Welcome to the coast, to the sea and the beautiful. This property is located as you can see directly by the sea. The property is modern and well-equipped and things that might delight the stay is a large private sauna, outdoor jacuzzi with sea view. Since the house is by the sea, there is a private jetty to swim from. Furthermore, there is a gas grill and a couple of different but large terraces with fatboys and hammock. To S√∂lvesborg it takes 10 minutes by car and to S√∂lvesborgs GK, this year's golf club, it also takes 10 minutes.

Cabin in Ronneby

5 out of 5 average rating, 6 reviews5 (6)

Cabin in the archipelago with your own dock, boat and hot tub

Small charming holiday home from the 50s with a sea plot, a private jetty and views of the Ronneby archipelago. Wood-fired hot tub and boat (without motor) included. The cottage is located at the far end of a peninsula and accessed by car. Nearby are shipyards, cafe and shop. Perfect stay for water activities, fishing, exploring nature or just relaxing. Garden with grass lawn for games and play. Trampoline is available. TV and Wifi are available. Guest access Full access to the whole house and grounds except for storage stalls.

Cozy cottage next to the sea edge

Welcome to Dansareviken, a quiet cottage area of 4 cottages with adjacent nature reserves with nice sandy areas and several barbecue areas. Here you can enjoy a fantastic view from both the living room and terrace. In the bay and around nearby islands there is the possibility of sun, swimming and fishing. A small boat with an electric motor is available. Cycling distance (about 5 km) to central Karlshamn. Please bring your own towels and bedding.

Seaside Home overlooking Blekinge Archipelago

Enjoy a wonderful stay exploring southern Sweden and the Blekinge Archipelago! This year-round house has magnificent views of the Spjako bay where you can enjoy both the sea and nature. The home has a large lawn, wooden deck with outdoor furniture and BBQ grill where you can enjoy your meals overlooking the sea. This is the perfect stay for water activities, fishing, exploring nature, or simply relaxing and enjoying the sunset!
